OL,3,CCoroner warns doctor about giving
OL,4,Cincriminating evidence at baby's
OL,5,Cinquest
OL,7,FA coroner has warned a doctor about
OL,8,Fgiving potentially incriminating
OL,9,Fevidence at a fresh inquest into the
OL,10,Fdeath of a premature baby.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, Robert Sowersby, assistant
OL,13,Fcoroner for Avon, was asking questions
OL,14,Fabout samples that appear to have been
OL,15,Ftaken from the body of Ben Condon.
