OL,7,FThe two-month-old died in the
OL,8,Fpaediatric intensive care unit of
OL,9,FBristol Children's Hospital on 17
OL,10,FApril 2015, six days after being
OL,11,Fadmitted there with a respiratory
OL,12,Fillness.
OL,14,FA previous inquest in June 2016
OL,15,Finitially established that Ben's death
OL,16,Fwas due to an acute respiratory
OL,17,Fdistress syndrome (ARDS),
OL,18,Fmetapneumovirus (hMPV) and prematurity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
