OL,7,FBut the following year, University
OL,8,FHospitals Bristol and Weston NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust admitted that their
OL,10,Ffailure to give Ben antibiotics for a
OL,11,Fpseudomonas bacterial infection had
OL,12,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,14,FHigh Court judges quashed the original
OL,15,Fconclusion in 2021 and - following
OL,16,Fcampaigning by Ben's parents Allyn and
OL,17,FJenny Condon - ordered a fresh
OL,18,Finquest, which began last Monday.
OL,20,FDoctor questioned about swabs
OL,21,Freportedly taken from Ben's body
