OL,7,FMr Sowersby was questioning Dr Matthew
OL,8,FChristopherson about a computer
OL,9,Fprintout of investigations undertaken
OL,10,Fin respect to Ben.
OL,12,FThe coroner said: "It appears from
OL,13,Fthis document that there are some
OL,14,Fsamples dated 18 April or 19 April, so
OL,15,Fafter Ben's death.
OL,17,F"Post-mortem sampling is regulated.
OL,18,FI'm going to ask you questions about
OL,19,Fthis."
