OL,7,FThe coroner told Dr Christopherson
OL,8,Fthat the doctor did not need to answer
OL,9,Fhis questions if he believed that he
OL,10,Fcould incriminate himself.
OL,12,FHe asked: "Did you take any post-
OL,13,Fmortem samples?"
OL,15,FDr Christopherson replied: "No, I did
OL,16,Fnot."
OL,18,FMr Sowersby then asked: "Did you know
OL,19,Fabout any samples taken from Ben after
OL,20,Fhis death?"
OL,26,@tD@KOUuD@PO]wD@\OUxD@EO]zD@YOU|D@KO]
