OL,7,FDr Christopherson said: "No, I did
OL,8,Fnot."
OL,10,FThe inquest previously heard how Ben's
OL,11,Fparents Allyn and Jenny Condon were
OL,12,Ftold a post-mortem examination was not
OL,13,Fnecessary following his death, and so
OL,14,Fthey chose to have his body cremated.
OL,16,FHowever, they later discovered that
OL,17,Ffour swabs had been taken from Ben's
OL,18,Fbody and sent for analysis after his
OL,19,Fdeath.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@EO]
