OL,7,FThe inquest heard that a different
OL,8,Fclinician - Dr Richard Brindle - had
OL,9,Fsent an internal email that mentioned
OL,10,Fthat the swab tests had been requested
OL,11,Fto "add useful information about the
OL,12,Fcause of death".
OL,14,FHowever, Dr Christopherson repeated
OL,15,Fthat he had no knowledge of the swabs:
OL,16,F"The last time I saw Ben was with Mr
OL,17,Fand Mrs Condon as I left the
OL,18,Fdepartment that evening."
OL,26,@sD@DOUtD@OO]xD@AOUzD@YO]
