OL,7,FBen's parents earlier told the hearing
OL,8,Fthey would not have cremated their son
OL,9,Fif they had known that the swabs had
OL,10,Fbeen taken, that he had a bacterial
OL,11,Finfection, or that he had been
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with ARDS.
OL,14,FThe coroner also queried why Dr
OL,15,FChristopherson and a colleague had
OL,16,Fbeen "confident" to record Ben's cause
OL,17,Fof death as ARDS caused by hMPV and
OL,18,Fprematurity, given the concerns that
OL,19,FBen may have developed a secondary
OL,20,Finfection.
OL,26,@xD@FOUxD@PO]
