OL,7,FDr Christopherson replied: "It was the
OL,8,Fsequence of events. He presented with
OL,9,FhMPV, if he hadn't had that, he
OL,10,Fwouldn't have become sick, he wouldn't
OL,11,Fhave developed ARDS and the subsequent
OL,12,Fcomplications of that."
OL,14,FHe added that he was not aware of
OL,15,Fresults identifying the pseudomonas
OL,16,Finfection at the time of Ben's death.
OL,26,@oD@\OUtD@WO]
