OL,7,FWhen asked about the death
OL,8,Fcertificate, he replied: "The culture
OL,9,Fat the time was to complete, where we
OL,10,Ffelt able to, the administrative sides
OL,11,Fof a child's death.
OL,13,F"This is because we recognised that
OL,14,Fthe death of a child is tragic. The
OL,15,Faim was to minimise as much distress
OL,16,Fas possible."
