OL,7,FOn Tuesday, the inquest heard that a
OL,8,Fdocument ` disclosed to family lawyers
OL,9,Fshortly before the beginning of the
OL,10,Ffresh inquest ` revealed concerns
OL,11,Fabout a possible infection two days
OL,12,Fbefore Ben's death.
OL,14,FThe document showed that a blood test
OL,15,Fmarked "urgent" had been ordered for
OL,16,FBen on that date, with "query sepsis"
OL,17,Flisted as the reason for the test.
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@OO]xD@XOUxD@eO]
