OL,7,FMr Sowersby asked Dr Christopherson
OL,8,Fwhether sepsis was a differential
OL,9,Fdiagnosis ` that's a list of
OL,10,Fconditions that could be behind a
OL,11,Fpatient's symptoms ` at that time.
OL,13,FDr Christopherson replied: "I expect
OL,14,Fit was on the differential diagnosis
OL,15,Flist. I have no more specifics to add
OL,16,Fto that."
OL,18,FThe inquest is expected to conclude on
OL,19,FFriday 21 February.
